      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-06-29/russian-ukraine-war-shapes-worldview-of-eu-s-new-chief-diplomat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡娅·卡拉斯在苏联占领爱沙尼亚期间长大，早在俄罗斯入侵乌克兰之前，她就敦促欧盟领导人认真对待俄罗斯的威胁]]></description>
